{
  "stem": "2097.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But that was later on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, he was only four, four and a 1/2 or five years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In home, we spoke Romanian and Hungarian-- but mainly Hungarian, because my mother, she didn't speak too well Hungarian-- I mean-- I'm sorry-- Romanian.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was born in a town where the Hungarians, they were more-- lived more-- I mean more Hungarians lived.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she grew up learning that language.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was raised in a city where I learned both languages.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Actually, the children, before they walk, they have to talk both languages.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before they walk, they have to talk the both languages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a big shock, because I spoke the language, but I didn't know how to write.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we got special teachers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because-- when the Hungarian occupied in 1940, the town-- not the town-- the area-- the whole part of Transylvania, by the-- the Hitler's decision-- Hitler was a chancellor in Europe, and conqueror.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- they brought-- the Hungarian brought in the Jewish law, where the Jewish children weren't allowed to study with the Christians.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we got special Jewish teachers from Hungarian, brought by the community to the school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were learning exactly the same thing as the others learned at the Christian gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the language was no problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the writing was a big problem, because we didn't know the Hungarian alphabet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's Latin letters, but it's different by the Romanian, because they have many, many words; and the O and the U of how you spell it-- long and short.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we coped with it, and we learned.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because we had to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And children-- they, somehow, adjust easier in their learning.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
